        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p>Original</p>
            <p>O<add>?</add> Rosalie (Duplicate) <hi rend="indent(1)"/><placeName>St.
                    Thomas</placeName> A H <date>Ab. 5604</date></p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isc Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Since my last of <date>13th</date>
                <add>?</add><lb/>
                <add>?</add> Brig Duca<add>?</add> via Ponce, I have been presented<lb/> attending
                to my business owing the severe <add>?</add><lb/> =sequent death of my beloved wife
                    <persName>Grace Sarah</persName><lb/> was taken from me on the <date>16th</date>
                    day<add>?</add> of <date>Janry</date> in her <add>?</add><lb/> year. her
                sickness was Consumption—I must yield<lb/> with resignation altho' the loss is very
                great, I have <add>?</add><lb/> with 2 daughters. The will of God be done—</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours of <date>May 17th</date> &amp; <date>June 11th</date> are at
                hand with books<lb/> all correct, I enclose herewith first of
                summoned<add>?</add><lb/> 16.00 <add>?</add> at 10 <add>?</add> on the
                    <persName>Mrss.Atwater</persName>
                <add>?</add>
                <placeName>New York</placeName> for<lb/> One hundred dollars which please pass to my
                credit <add>?</add><lb/> the capt of the “Rosalie” will take freight I will send
                the<lb/> Bay Water required, please have a plate engraved<lb/> at last for
                    <persName>D Alverty</persName> and send 300 cards with the<lb/>
                <add>?</add> always retaining the plate. <add>?</add><lb/> been suspended &amp; I
                believe will never ascend the <add>תיבה</add><lb/>
                <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>
                <add>?</add> Hazan he has worked is own <add>?</add><lb/> charge against him are
                very serious at the <add>השכבה</add>
                <add>?</add> poor<lb/> wife he refused to call her by my name, &amp; called her
                by<lb/> her fathers name, giving us his <add>?</add></p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>I have not yet received one cent on Acct of the<lb/> 2nd Vol of the Occident. Please
                add on the rest of<lb/> subscribers <persName>Mr A Senior</persName> of
                    <placeName>Aguadilla</placeName> P<add>?</add> &amp; <persName>Mr<lb/> Hy
                    Helmann</persName> of <placeName>Angostura</placeName> both for the 2nd
                Volume.<lb/> I hope soon to obtain more. take off <persName>Mr
                    O<add>?</add></persName><lb/> The Rosalie does not take freight—the 2 dozen<lb/>
                spelling books are gone to <placeName>Curaçao</placeName>—I want more.<lb/> The
                information from <placeName>Curaçao</placeName> &amp; the main has<lb/> not yet
                reached me. I anticipate getting some<lb/> purchasers for the Per<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>A Wolff</persName> has resigned as President because<lb/>
                he finds that his darling Idol <persName>Carrillon</persName> is op<lb/> =posed by
                the majority of the community.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Without further subject I remain</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Your friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">M B Simmons</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <date>July 19</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The foregoing is duplicate of my last.<lb/> I want some “Cathecisms”
                &amp; first books for<lb/> young children easier than the Cathecisms.</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">MBS</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <addressee>Revd Isc Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)"><add>?</add> Emily</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">via <placeName>N York</placeName></p>
        </body>
